posts.title: git push远端推送失败解决 error: remote unpack failed: unable to create temporary object directory
posts.text: 摘要 git裸仓推送出现错误 解决方案 fatal: sha1 file ‘‘ write error: Broken pipeerror: remote unpack failed: unable to create temporary object directory 为目录添加写权限sudo chown -R server-username 'git init目录' sudo chown -R server-username '/.../xx.git'
